            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>130/4/5</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Dl9q" id="i-웹-30의-개요">I. 웹 3.0의 개요<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/web-3-0#i-%EC%9B%B9-30%EC%9D%98-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2>
