<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Dl9q" id="iii-nft-비교">III. NFT 비교<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/nft#iii-nft-%EB%B9%84%EA%B5%90" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2>
<table><thead><tr><th>구분</th><th>FT</th><th>NFT</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>토큰 정보</td><td>토큰 이름 및 약어</td><td>고유 정보</td></tr><tr><td>상호 교환성</td><td>O</td><td>X</td></tr><tr><td>분할성</td><td>O</td><td>X</td></tr><tr><td>활용</td><td>송금, 물품 구매</td><td>자산 소유권</td></tr></tbody></table>]]></content:encoded>
