        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[퍼블릭, 프라이빗, 하이브리드 블록체인]]></title>
            <link>https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain</link>
            <guid>https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain</guid>
            <pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 02:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Public, Private, Hybrid Blockchain]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Dl9q" id="i-블록체인-개요">I. 블록체인 개요<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain#i-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9D%EC%B2%B4%EC%9D%B8-%EA%B0%9C%EC%9A%94" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li>개념<!-- -->
<ul>
<li>탈중앙화된 P2P 네트워크를 기반에 합의알고리즘을 통해 무결성을 제공하는 분산 원장 기술</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>배경</li>
</ul>
<table><thead><tr><th>도입기</th><th>발전기</th><th>확산기</th><th>정착기</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>디지털자산</td><td>스마트 계약</td><td>프로토콜</td><td>암호화폐/결제</td></tr><tr><td>거래 결제</td><td>지분증명</td><td>인터페이스</td><td>블록체인 기반 서비스 확대</td></tr><tr><td>비트코인 탄생</td><td>이더리움 탄생</td><td>알트코인 탄생</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>Public</td><td>Private</td><td>Hybrid</td><td>융복합</td></tr></tbody></table>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Dl9q" id="ii-구성">II. 구성<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain#ii-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_Dl9q" id="iii-적용방안">III. 적용방안<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/convergence/public-private-hybrid-blockchain#iii-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%EB%B0%A9%EC%95%88" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h3>
